Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚做了个奇怪的梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I just had the strangest dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是在星期五\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是医院 应该算是森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But it's not a hospital, it's a forest of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在你的身旁有一头熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And I know that because right next to you there's a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一头灰熊 把脚伸到小溪里冲凉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}A grizzly, cooling his feet in a stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,突然之间 你就开始分娩...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And all of a sudden, you begin to deliver...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而我不在你身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...and I can't get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是熊在你的身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But the bear can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,过了一会儿...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And next thing I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他就抱着我们漂亮的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...he is holding our beautiful baby boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的是就怪了! 噢 ....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And here's where it gets odd. Uh....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它咬断了脐带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He chews the cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但奇怪的是 我对此并不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But, strangely, I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这一定是个好兆头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's gotta be a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,希奥多 这名字好是好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Theodore. Loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,记得那篇给孩子取名的文章吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But remember that article I told you about? Naming kids after famous people?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这会让泰德将来背上 很大的成功压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I don't want Teddy to think he's a failure if he doesn't wind up on Mount Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 亚瑟 噢!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Uh, Arthur. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这不好念 这个名字有神话 古典的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This was tough, because it's mythological. Round Table, the whole deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你记得" 名字游戏 "吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But "The Name Game." Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"名字游戏" ?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}"The Name Game"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"亚瑟 Art- bo- Bart 香蕉 Fana- fo- Fart "\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}"Art- Art- bo- Bart, Banana- Fana- fo- Fart."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后还有凯西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Brings us to Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,以及很多名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This whole next slew of names:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,凯西 乔丹 狄伦 德鲁 泰勒 应该还有史盖勒...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Casey, Jordan, Dylan, Drew, Taylor, Tyler and probably mostly Skylar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都像是女孩的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...are all names that could be girls' names.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不干脆点 直接给他取个女孩的名字呢?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why don't we just cut to the chase and call him Cindy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我真想离开亚特兰大这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah, Atlanta. Trying to get out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能去丹佛就好了 - 嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Denver's where it's at, man. - Mm- hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有很多政府丑闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}They got the whole underground government conspiracy thing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗? - 我在网路上....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- That so? - I'm hearing a lot of chatter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看到很多传言 - 对不起 接个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- ...on the message boards. - Gotcha. I should grab this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 喂 宝贝 - 嗨! 老公\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Sorry. Hey, honey. Hey, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有收到我的留言了吗? - 收到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Did you get my message? - I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到一半 就累到不行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm about halfway through it. I thought I'd take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 我并不是说这些名字不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ha, ha. I didn't want you to think I was arbitrarily dismissing those names.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也考虑的很仔细\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You considered them carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这是个大事 知道吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's just such a big decision, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 你把这当成天大的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I know. Clearly, you're taking it very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,更重要的是 你现在穿着什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}More importantly, what are you wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阿曼尼 西装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Armani Exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是问我的...不 不 我在和司机说话 宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm talking to my... No, no, that's just the driver, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我要下车了 我挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay, listen, I'm about to be dropped off. I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爱你 很想早点见到你 - 我也爱你 一路顺风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I love you, can't wait to see you. - I love you too. Safe flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到了 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Here you go. - Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What in the eff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 该死的! - 一下撞了上来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Goddamn it! - We done knocked it right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 老兄! 你刚刚撞了我的车!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, man! You just hit my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你刚把我的车门撞掉 老兄 - 很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You just knocked my door off, man. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还好没伤到人吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}First things first, is everybody okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是辆豪华轿车! 你不知道机场行车的规矩吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm in a Town Car! Don't you know airport protocol?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,豪华轿车总是有优先权!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Town Cars have the right of way always!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一些严重破损\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That right there is some serious damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是小事!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That ain't shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我姐夫肯定发飙 没完没了!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My brother- in- law is gonna kill me. I'm through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没伤到你吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我朋友不好 他喝了点酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sorry about my friend. He's been drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一身酒味 你们边喝酒边开车吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You smell boozy too. Drinking and driving together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我们没一直喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, we haven't been drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 只喝了6罐啤酒 但是 ....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I mean, we split a six- pack. Of 40s. But....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲常说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My father always had a saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早就倒楣时 这天都会有好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}When a day starts like this, it's all uphill from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这话实际上是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's actually incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爸爸常这么说 - 不 应该是这一天都会有霉运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- My dad used to say it. - No, it's all downhill from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都希望有好运 没人希望有霉运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Everybody wants to be up. Nobody wants to be down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是霉运的可能性更大 你爸根本就是胡说八道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's easier as you go down. He didn't know what he was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喂 谢尔比? 怎么样 - 我们没事 老兄 我能处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Hey, Shelby? We good? - We're cool, man. I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 - 你去吧 大明星!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Okay. Go get them, Hollywood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,喂! 先生 你把我的行李撞倒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Excuse me. Sir? You mind picking these up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在机场我不能接触 其他人的行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I can't. You're not supposed to touch other people's luggage at an airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己的行李 自己处理吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Handle your own baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,检查行李!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Bag check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生 这你的包吗? - 对 有什么问题?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- This your bag, sir? - Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要搜查一下 先生 - 好的 请便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm gonna have to search it real quick, sir. - Yeah. Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,幽默杂志吗? 你可真行啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Mad magazine? That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是你的包吗? - 那不是 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- This is your bag? - That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好东西喔!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那绝对不是我的 我一定被那家伙掉包了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's definitely not mine. My bag got switched with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是你亲自装的行李吗? - 但不是这个包啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You packed your bag yourself? - But not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未吸过毒 这真是荒唐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I've never done drugs in my life. This is absolutely... This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定是贩毒的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Maybe you a drug mule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么 我看起来像是贩毒的? - 难说喔 毒贩子长怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Do I look like a drug mule? - I don't know, how do drug mules look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你比我清楚 - 像我这模样吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You're the expert. - What, like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我可没说 - 但你的眼神里有这意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Who said that? - Your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神? 我可没说 我不觉得你模样看起来像....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My eyes said something? Did my mouth? I don't think you look like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要这么乱翻好不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Do you mind not tossing it up so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,呜! 你这小子可真时髦啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Whoo! Funky motherfucker, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样回应非常不得体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You are so inappropriate, it's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别人对我有很多评价 不过说我 "不得体"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I been called a lot of things, but "inappropriate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那还是破天荒 头一回哩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's some fucked- up shit, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看这 宝贝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Look at this, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,多豪华\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在天堂里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Died and gone to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,难到你看不见 这里坐着一个人吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Are you not aware that there's a person here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是你啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么来头等舱了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What brings you up to first class?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的位子....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The seat that I procured...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 抱歉 - 借过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, sorry. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来在三等舱 但是我的安全带 坏了 就把我安排到头等舱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I was in low class, and my seat belt didn't work, and they bumped me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是经济舱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's called economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天日子真幸运 很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Lucky day. Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 刚认识的时候有些不愉快....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sorry how we met, but, you know....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们好像拿错了行李 - 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I think we switched our bags at the curb. - I know we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你的包被没收 里面有私人物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Your bag was confiscated. It had paraphernalia in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大烟枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Marijuana pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那是一种医疗仪器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, that's a medical apparatus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我患有青光眼 - 得了吧 你有青光眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I have glaucoma. - Sure, you have glaucoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,各位乘客请注意 在起飞以前 请关闭所有电子仪器 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Attention, in preparation for takeoff, please turn off all electronic devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有笔记型电脑 请收起来 感谢合作 祝你旅途愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...and if you have a laptop, please stow it. Thank you and enjoy your flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,刚广播了 你应该关掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}They made the announcement. You should turn that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 我听到了 - 你就关掉吧 知道为什么吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Yeah, I get it. - Just turn it off. You know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这就关掉 - 这是因为他们不安 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm gonna turn it off. - They get uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们知道恐怖分子经常用 手机引爆行李里的炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...because they know terrorists use their phones to trigger bombs in their luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 嘘 嘘~\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Shh. Pst, pst, pst.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这句话不能胡乱说 - 哪句话"恐怖分子"还是"炸弹" ?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- That's not the word you want to say. - "Terrorist" or "bomb"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你两句话都说了 - 这我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You said both the words. - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我只是想告诉你... - 不用你说 听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm trying to tell you that I read... - Stop trying to tell me and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不该说引起别人恐慌的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Don't say words that put people on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我只是想让你知道 - 这很不礼貌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm trying to be informative. - It's not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 对不起 你能和你的朋友 来一下吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Would you and your friend mind stepping to the front of the plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 我需要你 跟我一起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm sorry, I need you to come with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我从未见过这个小丑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Listen. This clown, I've never seen before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我们在路边调换过行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's not true. We switched bags at curbside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是不小心的 而他... - 先生!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- That was an accident. And he had... Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是联邦空警 请到飞机前面来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Federal air marshal. Please step to the front of the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 为什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,放下装置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Drop the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这不是什么装置 它是手机 - 放下装置! 浑蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- It's not a device, it's a BlackBerry. - Drop the device!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能对我开枪不成 冒牌警察?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What are you gonna do, rent- a- cop? Shoot me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大家不要惊慌 他不要紧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's okay, everyone. He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是橡胶子弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's only a rubber bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息 海曼先生 在飞机找到你的行李\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Good news, Mr. Highman. They found your bags on the airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 好啊 - 遗憾的是 飞机已在堪萨斯州上空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Oh, good. - Unfortunately, that plane's over Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不出所料 - 不过你的手机在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Figures. - But I do have your cell phone for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 请你在这文件上签字 就是释放文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Now, if you wouldn't mind just signing this. It's a simple release.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,避免我被起诉?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}So I don't sue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对 写的是我们都次依法行事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Just saying we acted in accordance with state law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Sure did. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里写下你的地址 我们好把你的行李寄回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}If you put your address there, I'll have your bags shipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 就留在洛杉矶机场吧 我去取 下一班航机是什么时候?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Let them land at LAX and I'll pick them up when I get there. When's the next flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一小时后 但你坐不上 - 为什么呢?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- ln an hour, but you won't be on it. - Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你被列入禁飞名单了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're on the No- Fly list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么? - 上面就这么写着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Why? - It says right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还有你的朋友 - 谁?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You and your friend. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我刚刚和他谈过 - 我从未见过那个浑蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- The gentleman I just interviewed. - I've never seen that dipshit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗? - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他可说了你不少好话 - 我在禁飞名单里? 真是可笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- He had nice things to say about you. - I'm on a No- Fly list? This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不加理会 ... - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Regardless... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子怀孕了 我必须回洛杉矶 这肯定是搞错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I have a pregnant wife, I have to get back. This is a huge misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能怎么办 - 你看过 阿甘正传吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What am I supposed to do? - Have you ever seen Forrest Gump?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他是走过去的 他是笨蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, he ran across country, and he was pretty stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我相信你比他强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}So I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're free to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,出了什么事?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What kind of incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我..也没什么啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm probably overstating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小事一桩 我能处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's the manageable kind. A micro- incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但遗憾的是 我被列入禁飞名单了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But it unfortunately landed me on a No- Fly list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么? 你对别人发脾气了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What did you do, Peter? Did you snap at somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不! 我没有 我自始至终都 很平静 克制情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Nope. I did not. I was cool, calm and collected the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没做任何出格的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I was completely in my rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你有时也容易冲动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You get so carried away sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎样回家?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How are you gonna get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个计画 而这个计画正在实现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I have a plan. And the plan is sorting itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不过我的钱包在飞机上 - 什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- But my wallet is traveling. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,身分证也在里面 我想租辆汽车 我记得办公室传真....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The ID's in it, I've been trying to rent a car, I had the office fax...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我正想尽办法去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But I am exhausting any and all opportunities to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿! 我一直在找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey! I've been looking all over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 离我远一点 你净惹麻烦 - 但是我捡到你的一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Stay away from me. But I found something of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 事情应该解决了 我先挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Honey, this might all be solved. I'll call you right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你有我的东西?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You got my stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在逮捕我之前 我拿到的 - 猴子?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I grabbed it before they zip- tied me. - Rally Monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我的钱包在你那里吗? - 我没看见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You get my wallet? - I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那我的行李呢?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Where's my bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你的行李 但是我拿不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I saw your bag, but I didn't grab it because my hands were full.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我的手上还拿着它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You know, I had this thing in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你租了哪辆汽车? - 没有 因为我没有驾照...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What kind of car did you get? - I didn't, because I don't have a license...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的钱包里 而钱包正在...对吧!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...because it's in my wallet that's on the.... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,靠夭哩 你还真是不走运 !!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, shoot. What a bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 不走运 !!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah, bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你把玩偶带来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Thanks for the doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真它妈的白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Fucking idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你想和我一起走吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, you wanna ride with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 我其实不是很喜欢狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No, I'm fine. I'm not really a big dog person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我知道我们 开始相处并不愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Look, I know we got off on the wrong foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不过了解我之后 你会发现我这人还挺不错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But I have a really great personality once you get to know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是啦 你能多好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah, I'm sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在脸书上有90个好友 有12个没加我 但毕竟有90位好友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I got 90 friends on Facebook. Twelve pending, but I got 90 friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,费用我来承担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'll cover expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们到了好莱坞时 你在还我也不迟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You can pay me back when we get to Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 洛杉矶 - 啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- L.A. - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那城市部叫好莱坞 叫洛杉矶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's not called Hollywood. It's Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我要去好莱坞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah, but I'm going to Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是伊森 伊森·崔布雷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My name's Ethan. Ethan Tremblay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而这个小家伙...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And this little guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这小胖子...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...this little butterball...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它叫桑尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...this is Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起走势我们的荣幸 来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And we would be honored to have you ride with us. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,会很有意思的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,开个玩笑 哈哈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}JK. LOL.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,上车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}"Hop in."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,世事难料啊 不是吗? 系上安全带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Life's weird, isn't it? Buckle up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有兄弟或者姐妹吗? - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You have any brothers or sisters? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有养狗吗? - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You have a dog? - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧问你个问题 你最喜爱的颜色是什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Let me ask you this: What's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蓝色 - 好酷喔 我喜欢绿色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Blue. - That's so cool. Mine's green.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哇啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢热狗吗? - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Do you like hot dogs? - Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我更喜欢玉米热狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm more of a corn- dog man, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经在裸体的海滩上吃过 一根老二形状得热狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I once ate a foot- long corn dog on a nude beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就吃过那一回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'll never do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你几岁不是处男? - 我不想谈论这个话题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- At what age did you lose your virginity? - I'm not gonna discuss that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是在 9 岁 - 小孩?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I was 9 years old. - Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个好女孩 好女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Great gal. Great gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,叫 "青春痘" 希拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sheila Pimples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点头痛 不是因为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm getting a headache, not because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是因为心事太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's just, I'm under a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆快要生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My wife and I are having a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 星期五是预产期 所以我买了猴子 - 噢 真的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- On Friday. That's who the monkey's for. - Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的 是剖腹产 - 真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Yep. C- section. - That's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以希望你能....感谢 - 我理解 完全理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- So if we could just.... Thanks. - I understand. God, I totally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去好莱坞见一位大经纪人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I was supposed to meet a bigtime agent in Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的是 他延后面会时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Luckily, he postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这么说你是演员 - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- So you're an actor. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆这样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yep. You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你帮我看看这几张造型如何啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}In fact, I wouldn't mind having a fresh pair of eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 喂 喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起! 你帮我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My apologies. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 你看着路 - 没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Okay. If you'd just look at the road. - I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 你的半身照 - 半身照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Oh, your headshots. - Headshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这张看上去像是悠闲的人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This one, this is a laid- back guy with a Hawaiian shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不过他带着一枝枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...but he packs a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有意思 - 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- lnteresting. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这张是我父亲最喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This one was my father's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他说这张最能表现我的性格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He says it really showed my spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,而我也这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And I agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What's that, a...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,分别是扮演黑社会 建筑工 和....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's a gang member, a construction worker, and....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一个书呆子 教授\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And a nerd. A professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我是扮演马尔科姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No. I'm Malcolm X.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它还真把自己当人 笨狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He thinks he's human. So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你来亚特兰大是生意还是旅游?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What brought you to Atlanta? Business or pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 生意 - 生意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Business. - Business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种生意?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What kind of business?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么进入建筑行业的? - 学这专业 还有其他问题吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- How'd you get into architecture? - College. Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果没有 我就吃饭了 - 对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Because I'm trying to... - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们毕竟要相处几天 认识一下彼此也是好的嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're gonna be traveling. It wouldn't hurt to get to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 你来亚特兰大 是生意还是旅游?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ethan, what brought you to Atlanta? Business or pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}My daddy died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我去亚特兰大是参加葬礼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I went to Atlanta to go to his funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 对不起 我不知道 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Gee, I didn't know. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人 老兄 是它让我去西部的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He was a great guy, man. That's why I'm heading out West.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是他激励我进入影视业的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He's the one that motivated me to get on the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 影视业吗? - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- TV? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要进入这一行不容易啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Tough business to break into.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,竞争很激烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}So competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我有位朋友 就干这一行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I have a friend, he's in that industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他演过 好汉两个半吗? - 没有 他....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Does he work on Two and a HalfMen? - No. He...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那太遗憾了 就是看了好汉两个半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's too bad. Because Two and a Half Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才想要做一名演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...is the reason I wanted to become an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吗 - 特别是第 2 季\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Right. - Especially the second season.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们计画这么走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Here's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚离开 伯明翰...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We are just outside Birmingham...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们动身有点晚 因此今天 只能刚进到路易士安那州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...and we got a late start, so we will only make it just to inside Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早点赶路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Early to bed, early to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,需要16至18个小时长途行驶 才能够到达亚利桑那州 菲尼克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Long 1 6- to 1 8- hour haul, which will land us in Phoenix, Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这样离洛杉矶就剩8小时车程了 - 你知道更好的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Eight hours outside of L.A. - You know what'd be nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们能在大峡谷停留一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}If we could stop at the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不去大峡谷 原因是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're not going to the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这比我们的最佳路线 多出120英里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That would be easily 1 20 miles off our optimum route.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那太遗憾了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我爸爸很喜欢大峡谷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Daddy would've loved the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还留着它?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why do you even have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 因为这就是我爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, because this is my daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,里面是他的骨灰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}These are his ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你把父亲的骨灰 装在咖啡罐里?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why are your father's ashes in a coffee can, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他死啊 彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Because he's dead, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这点我知道啦 - 我的话你都没听见吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I know. I know that part. - Don't you listen to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说 一般都放在骨灰坛里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm just saying, normal people put remains in an urn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是真空密封的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This is vacuum- sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,当你倒出咖啡时 就打开密封盖了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You broke the seal when you poured out the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,装上你父亲的骨灰再盖上盖子 那不叫真空密封\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You poured your father's remains in and closed it. That didn't reseal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没听过这么愚蠢的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's the dumbest thing I've ever heard in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我们不该来这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}God. We shouldn't have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我对蛋奶烘饼过敏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm allergic to waffles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来 桑尼 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Come on, Sonny. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在伯明翰 简短停留一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We need to make a brief pit stop in Birmingham.
