Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你能带着我们一起走吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Can you take us with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不过有个专门的 儿童权利保护机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No, but there's an organization called Child Protective Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么? - 是条领带 你从未看过领带吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What's this? - It's a tie. You've never seen a tie before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么系领带?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why do you wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Because I wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 看起来傻呼呼地 - 嗯 不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- It looks stupid. - Well, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Just take your hands off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Please stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,放手 请不要这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Stop. Please stop doing that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我没碰你 是它碰你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Will you please...? - It's Reggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.24,0:22:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗? 那就让它歇一会吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Is that right? Well, maybe Reggie needs to take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 放手 我是认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, quit it. I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了? 小家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You okay, bubba?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了 - 没什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"没什么" 就对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}"Nothing" is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你来告诉我 你说..\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And now, you come to me and you say:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"唐 科里奥 为我主持公道吧 "\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}"Don Corleone, give me justice."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你甚至没有叫我 教父\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But you don't even have the decency to call me the Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,并且你到我家里...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And you come to my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我女儿结婚的这一天...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...on the day that my daughter is to be married...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我去杀死某人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...and you ask me to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还是为了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}For money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.26,0:23:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是公道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But that is not justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真是厉害 第二段听得我热血沸腾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's amazing. I had chills, like, that second paragraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那段台词 那段谋杀 真是精彩 伊森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}When the line... The murder. That is so fucking good, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我还一直在研究用 什么样的手势效果最好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Thank you. I've been working on the hand gestures to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你自己写得吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Did you write that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不! 是黑手党写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No. The Mafia wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 原来如此.... 无论如何 很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, that was so... It was nice meeting you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,老实点 否则我还揍你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Play it cool, or I'll thump you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 不客气 你准备好了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sure, sure. You all set?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 可以走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah. Good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这两个孩子都听话吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How were they? They behave themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,听话 真听话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Pretty much. Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 那就好 - 是的-\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, good. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 他们都是好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I mean, they're great kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.17,0:23:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见 祝你好运 - 再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- See you. Good luck. Bye- bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.63,0:23:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你演艺事业取得成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Good luck with your acting stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.20,0:24:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...正判断性格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...is judging the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当一名演员在拍摄之前...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}When an actor is preparing a scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.17,0:24:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要做的是把剧本 看读很多遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...first thing is read the scene over many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.67,0:24:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,先不要让剧本适合自己 先让自己适应剧本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}First, before you do any work on it, let it work on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.84,0:24:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一遍一遍的读看 如果可能的话 看整部剧本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Read the material over and over again. The entire script, if at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.76,0:24:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 大明星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,信用卡被拒绝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Card's been declined.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.64,0:24:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 你的信用卡 里面没钱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What's that? - Your card? It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.52,0:24:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 天呀 - 没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Oh, gosh. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 肯定是租这辆车时 钱都花出去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You know what? I bet I tapped it out when I rented this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.36,0:24:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那就支付现金吧 你身上有多少钱?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Great. We'll pay cash. How much you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.86,0:24:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,60块钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sixty bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.53,0:25:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你总共就只有60块钱?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You have 60 bucks entirely?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啊 - 你买大麻花了多少?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Yes. - How much did you spend on marijuana?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.08,0:25:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在你的药上 - 不晓得 大概在200块钱左右\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- On your medicine? - I don't know, around 200 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.62,0:25:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 200块钱? - 对啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Two hundred bucks? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.12,0:25:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一路上加油 吃饭 住宿 一切就靠这 60块钱吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sixty bucks for gas, food, lodging, everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.58,0:25:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当地只有她手上有货 价格肯定要高一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}She's the only dealer in town. She names her price.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.09,0:25:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你几乎把所有钱都用来买毒品 你当时是怎么想的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What were you thinking when you spent almost all of our money on drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.51,0:25:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没想到吃饭 住宿的事 - 那你在那想到什么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I don't think in those terms. - What terms do you think in?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.26,0:25:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不是会计 甚至不是犹太人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm not an accountant. I'm not even Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.60,0:25:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你总该是个成年人? - 那当然 我都23岁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Are you an adult? - Of course I'm an adult. I'm 23 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.89,0:25:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,从没见过你 这么愚蠢的23岁的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You are the most shot- out 23- year- old I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.06,0:25:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么活到这么大的? 怎么没被车碾过去?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How have you made it? How have you not run yourself over?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.65,0:25:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我被有碾过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I've done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么活到现在的? 我的真是不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How have you survived? That's my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.74,0:25:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 主要靠运气 - 对喔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Mostly luck. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.40,0:25:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也这么想 你也只有靠运气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's what I thought. Just dumb fucking luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.57,0:25:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我操 - 干什么啊? 彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Fuck me. - Whoa! For heaven's sakes, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们完了 伊森 - 为什么会这样说?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- We're screwed, Ethan. - How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你把钱都用来买大麻了! - 这只是小小的挫折\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You spent all our money on weed! - It's just another speed bump.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.58,0:25:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗? 我还是给我老婆打电话 让她给我汇款 就这么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You know what? I'm gonna call my wife. She's gonna wire me money. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.25,0:25:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她不能 你没有身分证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}She can't. You don't have an lD.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:26:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对 那就汇给你 看见吗? 这才是成年人处里问题的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}She'll wire it to you. See? That's an adult solving a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.93,0:26:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们走吧 - 我就说嘛 我运气好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Let's go. - I told you I was lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.22,0:26:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你就上车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.10,0:26:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 我去买本杂志做简报用 好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hold on one second. I'm gonna go get a brochure for my scrapbook, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.48,0:26:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的姓怎么拼写? - T- R- E- M- B- L- A- Y\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- How do you spell the last name? T- R- E- M- B- L- A- Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.86,0:26:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 500美元 伊森·崔布雷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Here we go. Five hundred dollars. Ethan Tremblay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.12,0:26:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要再看 身分证明就可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I just need to see an ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.33,0:26:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿 给您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.42,0:26:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 上面写的不是 崔布雷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah, this doesn't say Tremblay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.59,0:26:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而是 伊森 雀斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It says Ethan Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.96,0:26:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天啊 他说的对 他是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, jeepers creepers. He's right, he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.01,0:26:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么意思 "他说的对" ?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What do you mean, "he's right"?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.80,0:26:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森·崔布雷是我的艺名 我是一名演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ethan Tremblay is my stage name. I'm an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.14,0:26:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的艺名 你真实姓名是什么? - 伊森 雀斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Your stage name. What is your real name? - Ethan Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.97,0:26:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做艺名不合适 - 你的本名更像是艺名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- It doesn't sound like an actor's name. - Ethan Chase does.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.14,0:26:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你的艺名算什么狗屁艺名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ethan Tremblay doesn't make any goddamn sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.48,0:26:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是编的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It sounds like it was made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.61,0:26:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 是我编的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah, I made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.02,0:27:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 我知道是你编的 但这是你的艺名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ethan, I know you made it up. It's your fucking stage name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.65,0:27:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么让我老婆把钱 汇到你艺名的名下?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why did you have my wife wire money to your stage name?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.36,0:27:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没考虑到 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I wasn't thinking. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.16,0:27:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我正尽力记住我的新名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Just trying to commit to the new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.87,0:27:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩有话去外面停车场说吧 别在这里谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Do you guys wanna discuss this, perhaps out in the parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.00,0:27:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就等一下 你有其它证明 你名字的东西吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}One sec. Do you have anything else with your name on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.13,0:27:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有啊 当然有 - 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Yes. Of course. - Yes, yes. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.84,0:27:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么没想到呢?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.67,0:27:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他有两个名字 - 那挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- He has two names. - That's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.22,0:27:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就等一下下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But one sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.10,0:27:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是干什么的? - 这是身分证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What the fuck is this? - It's an ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.81,0:27:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是张照片证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's a photo lD.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.64,0:27:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 这个也不能接受 - 为什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- No, I can't accept this either. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.77,0:27:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这只是一张你自己的照片 任何人能拍的照片...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Because it's a picture of yourself. Anyone could take a picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,穿件圆翻领服装 随便写上名字 并不能证明你的身分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...in a beautiful turtleneck, put whatever name they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.03,0:27:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不至于费这么大劲 就为了诈骗区区500元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But why go to all that trouble just for 500 bucks?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.36,0:27:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那可就难说了 但什么样的人没有啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I don't know why you would, but you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.49,0:27:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那我只能让我怀孕的妻子 开车去银行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}So I get to call my pregnant wife and have her drive all the way to Western Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.66,0:27:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,重新汇款 把它送到正确的名下...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Start this whole process all over again, send it to the correct name...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.33,0:27:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是这样?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...and we'll be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.54,0:28:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 正确 - 那好办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Absolutely. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.50,0:28:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但只能到明天了 我再 5 分钟后就下班了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We'll have to do that tomorrow. We close in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.38,0:28:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才 6︰35 先生!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's 6:35, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.55,0:28:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你是老板 你是干什么的? 上下班时间你说了算?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What are you, my boss? You make the hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.72,0:28:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我说5分钟后就下班 在饭店订了位 要和朋友 小孩们吃饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I say when we close. I got reservations at Chili's. I'm meeting my boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.72,0:28:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就因为你要赶饭局? - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You have a reservation at Chili's? - Mm- hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.39,0:28:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,提前预订好 聪明 星期三晚上饭店人比较多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's actually smart. I mean, it gets busy on a Wednesday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.61,0:28:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么一直瞪着我看?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Are you gonna stare at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.02,0:28:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你就不愿 尽自己的工作职责?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Do your fucking job until your shift is over, hillbilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.90,0:28:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尽你的头啊 你就别指望了 - 喔 真的吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Keep dreaming, faggot. No way in hell. - Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.70,0:28:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起!! 让我来吧 彼得 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Excuse me, Peter. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.12,0:28:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我替我的朋友抱歉 我们真的只需要点钱到洛杉矶...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm sorry about my friend. We really just need the money to get to Los Angeles...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.08,0:28:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他的第一个孩子 马上就要出生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...so he can be there for the birth of his first child.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.12,0:28:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,说的很动听 你知道我女儿出生时我在哪里吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's such a sweet story. You know where I was when my daughter was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.75,0:28:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 饭店里? - 伊拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Chili's? - Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.13,0:28:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,难道就因为女儿要出生 我就能擅离职守吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How about I call my sergeant in Fallujah and tell him your story, see what he thinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.30,0:28:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是要下班吗?怎么还说个没完?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Aren't you closing? Is it gonna take a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.14,0:28:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他是胡说八道 伊森 自称是什么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He's being sarcastic, Ethan, and also letting us know...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.97,0:28:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,久经沙场的战士 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...that he's a "battle- hardened" veteran...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.48,0:29:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,其实顶多去伊拉克游览绕一圈 逢人就吹嘘说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...who did some half- assed tour and talks about it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.65,0:29:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你放屁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你真行 - 你真变态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Smooth move, that. - You're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.23,0:29:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你这下惨了 小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You fucked up. Bigtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.82,0:29:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我惨了? - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I fucked up? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.66,0:29:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么惨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I fucked up bigtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.16,0:29:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你吐痰在自己的窗子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You spit on your own window.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.24,0:29:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们走吧 - 喂 小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Let's get out of here. - Hey, sport?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.96,0:29:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我去伊拉克游览绕了一圈?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What were you saying about my half- assed tour of duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.96,0:29:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起 我真不知道 - 不知道什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm sorry. I had no idea. No idea what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.67,0:29:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是残障吗? - 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm handicapable? - Handicapable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.34,0:29:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么可能知道? - 我不知道 真对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- How could you know? - I couldn't know, and I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.63,0:29:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说 这都怪我 说实在的 我只是今天心情不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Can I tell you something? Honestly, it's my fault. I'm just having a bad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 今天心情不太好? - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You had a bad day? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.01,0:29:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,更惨的 还在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's about to get a whole lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.43,0:29:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啦 把东西收起来 - 救命!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Okay, now put that away before you... Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.69,0:29:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 这一下很疼吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, I know that shit hurt, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.44,0:29:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啊~浑蛋 - 噢 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Ah. Fucking hick. - Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.98,0:29:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看不出我有两下子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The kid's got moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.32,0:29:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让我赶不上饭局 我就让你爬不起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You wanna fuck up my dinner plans, I'll fuck you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.49,0:29:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这招我称之为" 独轮车 "\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I call that little move "the wheelbarrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.70,0:29:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 彼得 快起来 起来 - 来啊 来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Peter, get up, get up. - Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.70,0:30:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这就是银行的待客之道 - 先住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Courtesy of Western Union, huh? - Hold on one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.79,0:30:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 你要去哪里? - 去报警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Oh, where you going, huh? Call the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.21,0:30:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,报什么警啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Fuck the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.79,0:30:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,火车来了 呜呜!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Here comes the train. Choo- choo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.84,0:30:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下班时间到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's closing time
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.84,0:30:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去赶饭局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Time to roll to Chili's
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.51,0:30:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,和朋友吃顿饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And chow down with my fuckin' boys
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.70,0:30:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧 伙计?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You okay, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.87,0:30:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫我哥们 哥们不会在我被揍时 在一边袖手旁观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Don't call me that. Buddies have each other's backs when an assault takes place.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.04,0:30:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 它是残障啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter, that man was handicapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.04,0:30:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以叫我彼得 或者海曼先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You can call me Peter. Or Mr. Highman.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.21,0:30:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你雀斯先生 除非你的身份证那也是假的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'll call you Mr. Chase. Unless that was a fake lD too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.55,0:31:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真不明白你要艺名要干什么 你又不是真正的演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why you have a stage name is beyond me. You're not really an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.56,0:31:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思? 什么叫做真正的演员?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What does that mean, "really an actor"? What is a real actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.60,0:31:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真正会表演才是演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}A real actor is someone who can really act.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.90,0:31:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那你说吧 让我表演什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, go ahead, give me an action to do. Give me a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.73,0:31:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我不想说 - 你应该说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- No. I don't want to. - You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.73,0:31:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 假如我是茱莉亚·罗伯茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay. I'm Julia Roberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.82,0:31:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你查出来患了绝症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You have terminal cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.95,0:31:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们即将结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.24,0:31:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你会怎样向我公布消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Break the news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.28,0:31:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚·罗伯茨 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Julia Roberts...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.33,0:31:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正如你所知 我们即将结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...as you know, we're engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.75,0:31:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我患了绝症\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I have terminal cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.25,0:31:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.46,0:31:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 抱歉 这就是我的评价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What? - Sorry, that's my feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.51,0:31:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得挺好 - 不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I thought that was really good. - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.68,0:31:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我再给你一个机会 假如今天是超级杯总决赛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'll give you one more shot. It's Super Bowl Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.30,0:31:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个职业生涯坎坷的教练\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're a coach with a spotty career.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.76,0:31:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你们落后31分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're down 31 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.48,0:31:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你在中场休息室 想要激起队员的斗志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Bust into the locker room and fire the guys up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.85,0:31:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让大家都拼了 开拍!!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}All or nothing. Action.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.81,0:31:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 傻了 怎么可能有这种电影 - 每两年都会有这样一部电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Stupid. That would never be in a movie. - It's in a movie every two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.03,0:31:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,每两年都会有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Every two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.28,0:32:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 队员们 我们需要到球场去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay, guys, we need to get out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.79,0:32:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的需要拼搏 波勒德 你打的什么球?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Really need to get going. Pollard, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.21,0:32:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,软弱无力 难道你是娘们吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're acting like a girl out there. What are you, a girl or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.17,0:32:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克逊 来啊 老兄你要振作起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Jackson, come on, man, you gotta get yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.34,0:32:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 难道你也是娘们吗?? - 再刺激你一下 你老婆来电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What are you, a girl or something? - Let's up the stakes. Your wife calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她想要和你离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}She wants a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.22,0:32:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 教练的老婆吗? - 你扮演的就是教练\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- The coach's wife? - The coach you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.14,0:32:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你老婆来电话 她想要离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}His wife calls. She wants a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.35,0:32:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,电话来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ring- ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.06,0:32:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.86,0:32:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,队员们 先等一下 是我老婆 她想要和我离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, fellas, it's gonna be a minute. It's my wife. She wants a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.53,0:32:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 老婆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.33,0:32:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.75,0:32:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不要..\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.50,0:32:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在正忙着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This is not a good time.
