Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.03,0:34:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他人缘极好 他热爱他的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He was a real people person. He loved his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.49,0:34:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他每天回家来 都笑着说 他的窗口汽车排的最长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He'd come home every night and he'd laugh about how long his line was.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.37,0:34:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为经过他的窗口 他都喜欢和别人聊上几句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Because he enjoyed talking to everybody that went through the toll booth.
