Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.14,0:35:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他到我的房间说 "披特 给你一个重要的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yep. Came into my room, said, "Petey, I got an important job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.77,0:35:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上5点半 把我叫醒 "\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I need you to wake me up, 5:30 tomorrow morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.48,0:35:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我特别高兴 他从未要我做过任何事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And I was ecstatic because he never asked me to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.03,0:35:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都以为他觉得我不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I didn't even know I existed in his eyes. So....
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.53,0:35:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他能交付我做事 于是我特别兴奋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It was just a big deal. I was so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.99,0:35:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,定了闹钟 也睡不着觉 我整夜看着闹钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I set the alarm clock. I could barely sleep. I just watched it all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.41,0:35:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,到了5点半时 我偷偷地进入他的房间...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}When it went off at 5:30, I snuck into his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.88,0:35:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,小心翼翼叫醒他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...I gingerly wake him up.
