Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.14,0:35:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 微笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...uh, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.10,0:35:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他的行李已经收拾好 放在前门旁边了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But he had his bags packed by the front door...
