Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.53,0:41:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在想..."彼得不可能 把我留在这里扔下不管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I was thinking, "There's no way that Peter would have left me here.
