Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.78,0:45:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但医生说过在开车的时候 不应该睡觉吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Did the doctor say it is not advisable to fall asleep while driving?
