Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.89,0:55:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,醇香\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Robust blend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.93,0:55:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的很喜爱咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He really enjoyed coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.27,0:55:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,结果最后却被人当咖啡喝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And in the end, he was enjoyed as coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.52,0:55:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真是生命的循环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Kind of circle of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.69,0:55:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,狮子王的主题曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Lion King. All that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.90,0:55:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 你问问题的禁令解除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'll tell you what, the moratorium on asking questions is officially lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.53,0:55:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你随便问吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Fire away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.29,0:55:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.79,0:55:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你胳臂怎么样了 - 还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- How's your arm? - Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.21,0:55:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得达里尔 与你老婆睡觉了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Do you think Darryl slept with your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.13,0:55:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不会 - 可我觉得有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- No. - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.55,0:55:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然他为什么 将豪华汽车借给你 ?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I mean, why would he lend you this very fancy car...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.38,0:55:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,并且还给你路费? 这是....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...and give you all that walking- around money? It's....
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.38,0:55:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他是我朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Because he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.55,0:56:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是这个原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.60,0:56:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你去过圣地牙哥动物园吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Have you ever been to the San Diego Zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.06,0:56:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问你个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.89,0:56:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你这三个问题有什么关联?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How did those three questions come into your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.40,0:56:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想了想 可能是达里尔 让你老婆怀孕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I was thinking about your wife and Darryl, Darryl getting your wife pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.23,0:56:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,生下的孩子就会像斑马一样 黑一道 白一道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What their baby would look like, maybe like a zebra baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.90,0:56:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我想 我还从未见过斑马\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Then I thought, "Well, I've never seen a zebra."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.41,0:56:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,于是觉得到了加州后 或许应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And I thought, "Well, I should maybe go to the San Diego Zoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.74,0:56:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去圣地牙哥动物园看看 - 我没去过那动物园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- ...when we get to California..." - Nope, I've never been to the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.00,0:56:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,问下一个问题吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Next question, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.50,0:56:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 老婆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.25,0:56:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爱慕 忠贞于你的老公 再德克萨斯州给你打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's your ever- faithful and adoring husband calling from West Texas.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.63,0:56:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只是问候你一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Just checking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.84,0:56:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪你没接电话 你正在与达里尔通话吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Weird, it went to voicemail. Are you on the other line with Darryl?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.35,0:56:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我实际上刚和他谈过...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I actually talked to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.60,0:56:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你们在圣地牙哥 度过了愉快的周末\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...and he told me about the lovely weekend you guys spent in San Diego.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.14,0:56:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这和你说的不太一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Didn't jibe with the way you recounted it...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.35,0:56:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩多发发电子邮件 打打电话...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...so maybe with all your e- mails and phone calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.27,0:56:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,争取口供一至\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...you can get your story straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.65,0:56:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么需要我知道的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}If there's something you need to tell me before we go down this road...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.11,0:57:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我一声 我会很感谢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...if I'm gonna have a surprise in the delivery room...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.82,0:57:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,免得孩子生下来之后 我再大吃一惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...I would just appreciate it that you erase any and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.33,0:57:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,给我回电话..\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.87,0:57:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有没有这回事? - 关于什么事?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Was I right or was I wrong? - About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.46,0:57:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,达里尔和你老婆的事 以及孩子父亲的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The Darryl thing, your wife, and the mystery about the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.46,0:57:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她睡了 我给她留言了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}She's sleeping. I left a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.22,0:57:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,另外你随便的说起这个话题 让我很不爽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And the casual manner with which you bring up this topic, it makes me edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.51,0:57:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因此希望你不要再这样了 我会感激你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}So if you wouldn't mind not doing that anymore I'd really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.35,0:57:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我买了些零食 - 我看见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I got some snacks. - Yes, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.35,0:57:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,遗憾的是 我需要你来开车 我吃了止痛药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Unfortunately, I need you to drive. I'm on Vicodin.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.19,0:57:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,会嗜睡 所以我不能开车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm not supposed to operate heavy machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.69,0:57:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I will tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.15,0:57:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你眼皮打架 甚至看起来像打盹 更别说睡着了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}If you blink, if you even look like you might be dozing, let alone fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.03,0:57:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要用你的围巾 勒死你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...I'm gonna put hands on you. I'm gonna choke you out with your own scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.54,0:57:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,用围巾缠绕你的脖子周遭 直到你咽气 我肯定做得到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Wrap that thing around your neck and choke you the fuck out. Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.67,0:57:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有点激烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Seems a bit drastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.42,0:57:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,摘掉你的墨镜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Take off your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.88,0:57:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,刚买的 怎样也要展示一下嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I bought them, I wanted to showcase them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.96,0:57:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是夜晚 你还要开车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's night. You're driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.80,0:58:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一点小车祸而已嘛 瞧你紧张的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You act like you've never been in a fender- bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.22,0:58:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 摘掉它 - 好啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Remove them. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.68,0:58:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 震动可乐? 把它喝了 - 没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Jolt Cola? Drink it. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.18,0:58:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别对我比手画脚 - 你喝了就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You're not the boss of me, you know. - I know. Just drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.73,0:58:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.69,0:58:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小金刚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.87,0:58:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说一下 我睡着那件事...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}By the way, when I fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.04,0:58:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也只有那么一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...that was a one- time occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.54,0:58:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是个成人 不用你操心 - 还有件事 你上过厕所了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I know what I'm doing. I'm a grown man. - Did you remember to use the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.38,0:58:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.02,0:58:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你 独自一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey you, out there on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.94,0:59:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一丝不挂的坐电话旁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sitting naked by the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.23,0:59:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你会触摸我吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Would you touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.70,0:59:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你 耳朵贴在墙上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey you, with your ear against the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.87,0:59:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等待别人的呼唤 你会触摸我吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Waiting for someone to call out Would you touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.42,0:59:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你 可以帮助我搬起石头吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey you Would you help me to carry the stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.59,0:59:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,打开心扉 我快回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Open your heart, I'm coming home
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.11,0:59:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是好东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This is some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.86,0:59:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这扇窗子打不开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This window is not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.32,0:59:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是我锁上 在里里熏一熏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No, I locked them so we could get a good clambake going on in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.79,0:59:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这样让桑尼也吸一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That way, Sonny could get stoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.96,0:59:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我吸毒了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Am I stoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.71,1:00:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉到了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Do you feel stoned?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.14,1:00:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可这只是幻想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But it was only fantasy
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.98,1:00:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他怎样努力 都无法挣脱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No matter how he tried He could not break free
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.32,1:00:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,虫子在腐蚀他的脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And the worms ate into his brain
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.75,1:00:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你 不要告诉我一线希望都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey you Don't tell me there's no hope at all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.59,1:00:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在一起 我们站起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Together we stand
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.89,1:00:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,分开了 我们倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Divided we fall
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.02,1:01:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢? 怎怎解决的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Then what? How did it resolve?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.36,1:01:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 后来发现乳酪研磨器 是在褥垫下面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, it turns out the cheese grater was underneath the mattress.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.41,1:01:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 哈!那如此复杂 又有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ha, ha! That is so sophisticated. And has heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.79,1:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,电视剧有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The show has heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.29,1:01:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么对此知道那么多?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How do you know so much about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.54,1:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我管理这个电视剧的一个粉丝网站 非官方的 我管理这网站约6年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I run a fan site for the show. Not official, but I've run a fan site for about six years.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.21,1:01:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,开始是在一间网吧建立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I started it at an internet caf?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.63,1:01:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,过去经常泡网吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Used to go in there and wash my feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.80,1:01:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什么网站?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What was the site called?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.38,1:01:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了 好汉两个半.com\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It'sRainingTwoAndAHalfMen.com.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.89,1:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哇呜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.43,1:01:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害 我能收回以前对你 所有不好的评价吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That is sublime. Can I retract every derogatory statement I've made about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.73,1:01:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 彼得 非常棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Thank you, Peter. That's very sweet.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.23,1:01:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我一块 - 当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Hand me a Bugle. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.32,1:01:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.78,1:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给狗也吃1块 - 好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Will you feed one to the hound? - Very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.32,1:01:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在高速公路上吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Are we on the highway still?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.24,1:01:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 彼得 我自有分寸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Relax, Peter, I've got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.45,1:01:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.79,1:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是因为吸了大麻 才疑神疑鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're getting paranoid. That pot got to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.33,1:02:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你看见那个标牌了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay. All right, you see the flag?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.80,1:02:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像边界牌 上面写着"墨西哥"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It looks like a border crossing, it says "Mexico"...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.51,1:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 天啊 - 又怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Oh, Lord. Gosh. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.59,1:02:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为是加油站 我们汽油不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I thought that said Texaco. We're low on gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.10,1:02:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 我们没事 - 没事?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Okay, we're fine. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.60,1:02:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没事 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're good. We're good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.31,1:02:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么说?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What are you gonna tell them?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.94,1:02:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我就说 "你看 我们弄错了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}All I'm gonna do is say, "Look, we made a mistake."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.44,1:02:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后要求调头转回美国 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- And we're gonna ask to turn around. - Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.65,1:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你坐直了 什么话都不要说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay, I need you to be quiet. Sit straight. Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.99,1:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们问我问题 我不说话岂不更可疑!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Won't that be suspicious if they ask me a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.78,1:02:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都让我处理吧 - 就交给你处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Let me handle everything. - You handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.95,1:02:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们去了 - 喔 他正看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Here we go. - Uh- oh. He's looking right at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.29,1:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 你什么话也别说 好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter, please be quiet, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.12,1:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.21,1:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 很不幸地 我们走错路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hello. The weirdest thing happened. We just kind of got shifted...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.38,1:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是美国公民吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Are you guys American citizens?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.80,1:02:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是的 我们都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yes. Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.34,1:02:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们两个吗? - 是的 绝对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- The both of you? - Yes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.30,1:02:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能看看你的护照吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Can I see your passports?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.47,1:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有护照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We don't have passports.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.51,1:03:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是我们没想到会来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The thing is, we didn't mean to end up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.85,1:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是走错路了 因此.... 然后就到这里来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Somehow, I must have taken the wrong exit, and we're here, so....
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.56,1:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我们调头转回去吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}If we could just maybe turn around and go back?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.82,1:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要调头转回去?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You wanna turn around?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.53,1:03:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们走错路 我们本来是要去....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Yeah, it was a mistake. We're trying to get back...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.86,1:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What's wrong with your friend?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.53,1:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 别这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.87,1:03:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛怎么发亮? 开派对了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why are your eyes so glassy? You been partying?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.33,1:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我有青光眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No, I have glaucoma.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.00,1:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友 他也有青光眼吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What about your friend, does he have glaucoma too?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.00,1:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,回答他 你有青光眼吗? 不 他没有青光眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Answer the man. Do you have glaucoma? No, he doesn't have glaucoma.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.34,1:03:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那狗也有青光眼吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What about the dog, does he have glaucoma?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.72,1:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它的眼睛也亮的很\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Because his eyes are glassy as fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.39,1:03:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,车子熄火 把钥匙给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Shut off the car. Give me the keys, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.77,1:03:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里等着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.44,1:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 被我搞砸了? - 不 没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Did I blow it? - No, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.36,1:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你真圆滑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You are smooth.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.49,1:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哇 - 把桑尼交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Wow. - Hand me Sonny, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.37,1:04:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我刚才吓的要命 心都跳到喉咙上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}God, my heart was in my throat. I was flipping out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.25,1:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把我父亲的骨灰给我 在地板上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Could you hand me my father's ashes? They're on the floorboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.00,1:04:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 你要做什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Wow. What's...? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.14,1:04:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走错了路 不小心地到了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We took the wrong exit, we wound up here by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.15,1:04:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你问我多少次 我还是这个回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No matter how many times you ask, that's my answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.69,1:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像是 杰森 柏恩一样 老兄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You sound like Jason Bourne, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.90,1:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道你要去哪儿 没有身分证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You don't know where you're going. No ID.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.15,1:04:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我想联系美国领事馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I wanna speak to the American consulate.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.45,1:04:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是美国人 我有权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm American, I have rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.95,1:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 当然 没错 - 谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Oh, yeah, sure. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.74,1:04:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 拉蒙 他要找领事馆谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey, Ramon. He wants to talk to his consulate.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.46,1:04:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 先生 欢迎到美国领事馆来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hello, sir. Welcome to the American consulate.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.34,1:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能帮你吗 - 这根本是胡闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- How can I help you? - That's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.93,1:05:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们笑什么? 这是严肃的事 我有权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What are you laughing about? This is a serious matter. I have rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.43,1:05:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们美国人偷渡进我们的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You americanos sneak into our country.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.76,1:05:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,带来了毒品 派对 还和我们的妇女睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You bring drugs, you party. You sleep with our women.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.77,1:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未听说过 美国人偷渡到墨西哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I've never heard of an American sneaking into Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.35,1:05:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个独立的意外事件 通常是偷渡到美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This would be an isolated incident. It's usually the reverse.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.11,1:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了 你吊儿郎当的态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm getting tired of your cavalier attitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.82,1:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 对不起 很对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, I apologize. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.95,1:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你试图把毒品运送过国际边境 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You attempted to transport drugs across an international border...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.95,1:05:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...dude.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.95,1:05:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不是小事啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This is serious shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.58,1:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这笨蛋以为这点大麻 就会让他坐牢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.12,1:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这大麻还真不赖
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.07,1:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然啰 治疗青光眼的大麻嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.99,1:06:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好 爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.45,1:06:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}There.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.23,1:06:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.53,1:06:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 浑蛋!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.71,1:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,停车!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.59,1:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.39,1:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.70,1:07:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 停到路边! - 天啊 怎么回事?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Pull over! - What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.78,1:07:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,把车停下来!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Pull the car over!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.13,1:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,坐稳了 桑尼 会有些颠颇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hold on, Sonny, it's about to get rough.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.59,1:07:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.45,1:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.96,1:08:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大明星!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hollywood!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.47,1:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 惨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, crud.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.15,1:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 彼得 你怎么样?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter? Peter, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.16,1:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们刚刚违反了多少条法律?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}How many laws did we just break?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.37,1:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 有60条吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I don't know, 60?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.41,1:08:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时不知道怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I had no idea where I was going.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.33,1:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我看见你 还有... 什么时候我们一起去...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Then I see you. Remember, when we jackknifed together?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.13,1:09:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是样子不像你 - 我们对视过一眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- But you didn't look like you. - We locked eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.63,1:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 靠 你的样子好疯狂! - 是啊 我是在隐身模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- God, you looked crazy! - Yeah. Well, I'm in stealth mode.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.63,1:09:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以才用围巾包着我的头 - 你当时就像个突击队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- That's why I got the scarf on my head. - You were like a commando.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.01,1:09:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你简直就是突击队员 - 谢谢夸奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You were a Comanche warrior. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.01,1:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是史上最牛的突击队员 - 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- It was the greatest ever. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.18,1:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不要动 准备好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Don't move. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.02,1:09:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么? 喔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.60,1:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的新半身像 哈哈哈!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's your new headshot. Ha- ha- ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.56,1:09:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是啊 - 瞧 这张多好看啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Yeah. - How could it not be?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.53,1:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 真是疼死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}God, the pain is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.20,1:09:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能把这张照片发送给我吗? - 好呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Will you e- mail that to me, please? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.57,1:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 别吃太多了 彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay. All right. Just not too much, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.83,1:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,营救 一次勇敢的营救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Rescue. A daring rescue.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.21,1:09:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你回来救我 - 那是当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You came back for me. - Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.33,1:09:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你真勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're so brave.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.92,1:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证过的 我说过要把你安全送回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I made you a promise. I told you I was gonna get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.76,1:09:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把你安全送回家 对吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm getting you home safe, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.26,1:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要吻你 - 什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm gonna kiss you. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.72,1:09:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要和你亲热一下 - 不要 !!!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm gonna give you a smooch. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.39,1:09:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 !! 宝贝 - 免谈 !\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Come on, baby. - No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.72,1:09:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我亲热一下 - 别闹了彼得 停止!我在开车呢!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Give me a little smooch. - Stop, Peter! I'm driving! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.56,1:09:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,变态!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sick!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.94,1:10:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亲到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.35,1:10:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么神经兮兮的 - 你对我有大恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Everything's up and down with you. - I owe you bigtime.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.86,1:10:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是你 我绝对见不到 孩子的出生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No way I'd see my kid if you hadn't done that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.44,1:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对没办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.24,1:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 哥们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I love you, dude.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.24,1:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你 彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I love you too, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.30,1:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.55,1:10:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老婆 我真的很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sweetheart, I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.60,1:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我这人总爱妒忌 又爱吃醋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You know how I get. I've always been jealous. It's....
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.77,1:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说过遇见他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You knew about that. I told you I ran into him there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.60,1:10:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 你没做任何错事 都是我不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I know, and I know it has nothing to do with you. It's just my shit. It's my shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.11,1:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的话 好吗? 不要说任何事 就听我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Just listen to me, okay? Don't say anything. Just listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.28,1:10:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不会背叛你 彼得 你是知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I would never betray you, Peter, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.78,1:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是一家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're a family now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.45,1:10:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别的都不重要 你明白吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Nothing else matters. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.41,1:11:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说的很对 - 你安全回家就行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You're so right. - Can you just get home safely, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.17,1:11:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爱你 宝贝 - 我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I love you, baby. - I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.48,1:11:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 伊森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Wake up. Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.82,1:11:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.30,1:11:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说 这不是我编的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm telling you, I wouldn't make it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.88,1:11:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你能肯定? 我听说它是人造峡谷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You sure? I could've sworn I read it was man- made.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.34,1:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 非常古老 是历史形成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Nope. Not correct. Very old. Formed over time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.68,1:12:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大峡谷 这是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Grand Canyon. Known fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.48,1:12:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 我记忆力很好 我记得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter, I have a photogenic memory. I have recall for...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.31,1:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,伊森 我可以保证大峡谷的历史 很古老了 这可不是胡佛大坝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Ethan, I promise you. It's old. It's the Grand Canyon, it's not the Hoover Dam.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.36,1:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道这不是胡佛大坝 那是朝圣者建造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, I know it's not the Hoover Dam, that was built by the Pilgrims.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.40,1:12:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也不对!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Also incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.32,1:12:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不过它很壮丽宏伟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's magnificent though.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.37,1:12:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道不必停下来 - 没关系 这里正好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You didn't have to stop, you know. - That's okay. It's the perfect place.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.41,1:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上路吧 我任何时候都能来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Let's hit the road. I can do that any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.58,1:12:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,时间多的是 明早再到洛杉矶也不迟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We've got time. We don't have to be in L.A. till morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.50,1:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必着急 放松\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What are you doing? Relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.05,1:12:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还是按我们原来的计画吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We should just stick with the plan, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.26,1:12:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但这不是你计画的一部分吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But I thought this was part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.89,1:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还是有别的原因?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What am I missing, Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.93,1:12:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What's really going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.97,1:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,当我说大峡谷不顺路时 你说︰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}When I said the Grand Canyon wasn't on the way, you said:
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.02,1:12:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"太遗憾了 要是能去就太棒了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}"Too bad, it would've been perfect."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.19,1:12:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们过了密西西比河后 你又说︰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}When we passed the Mississippi River you said:
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.57,1:12:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"太遗憾了 我爸喜爱爵士乐和乳房"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}"Too bad, Dad loved titties and jazz."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.48,1:12:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我只不过是...我们还有事做做 而且我不想要耽搁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I just... You know, we got stuff to do and I don't wanna step on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.91,1:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不愿和父亲告别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I know it's hard to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.41,1:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然不认识你爸爸 但是根据你所说的 他是位好父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And I didn't know your dad, but from what you've told me he was a great father.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.95,1:13:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He was a cool guy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.12,1:13:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm just saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.96,1:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm just suggesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.59,1:13:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不能把他喝到肚子里...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}If you got it in you...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.42,1:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,应当给他一个体面的归宿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...he deserves a grand gesture.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.60,1:13:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.40,1:13:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 桑尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Come on, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.57,1:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来 宝贝 来这里 对啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Come here, sweetheart. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.63,1:14:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你我情同父子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Dad, you were like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.64,1:14:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,另外...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.14,1:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你我真不知道自己 能不能成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...I don't know how I'm gonna make it without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.86,1:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我知道你将会在天堂照看我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But I know that you'll look after me from up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.32,1:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你失望 爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm gonna make you proud, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.20,1:14:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.91,1:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.04,1:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.38,1:14:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,替我问候妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Say hi to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.85,1:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Bye, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.20,1:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个好人 如同我一样 你肯定会喜欢他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}He was a great guy. You would've loved him. He was just like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.46,1:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Hey....
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.96,1:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我对不起你 一直想告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}There's something I've been wanting to tell you I feel pretty awful about.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.59,1:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这些话不吐不快 我....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I kind of want to get it off my chest. I....
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.60,1:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在公路休息站的时候 我确实抛弃了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I ditched you at the rest stop in Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.48,1:15:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 本来不想回头的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What? - I had no intention of coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.27,1:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}So wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.94,1:15:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何这么做?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.40,1:15:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是个混蛋 我正在改\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Because I'm a pig. I'm an asshole. I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.11,1:15:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但你知道嘛 你毕竟带着早餐回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, you know what? You came back with doughnuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.41,1:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这就能够抵消 你把我抛弃了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I think that says more about you than leaving does.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.04,1:15:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.16,1:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这事就...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...just...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.37,1:16:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是大肚 感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're something else. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.00,1:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就轻松多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That's a load off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.13,1:16:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我也有件事不吐不快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Well, there's something I've been wanting to get off my chest too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.05,1:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.47,1:16:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实不是23岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm not really 23 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.43,1:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.48,1:16:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.15,1:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其它事情是 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The other thing is...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.99,1:16:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 ...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...Peter...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.11,1:16:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的钱包一直在我这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...I have your wallet and I've had it this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.99,1:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.62,1:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.79,1:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.71,1:16:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 听我解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...okay, listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.54,1:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么这么做?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.50,1:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我在飞机上看到你的钱包 不想要一个人走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I saw it on the plane and I didn't wanna be alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.63,1:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲去世了 我感到无依无靠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I was feeling vulnerable because of my father's death.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.64,1:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不想要一个人走这么远的路 你知道吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And I just didn't wanna go across country by myself, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.52,1:17:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 东西全部都在 - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- It's all here. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.23,1:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,钱 信用卡 一切用的着的 全部都在....\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}All my money, all my credit cards. Everything....
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.90,1:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都没少!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Everything I needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.86,1:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在你那里!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}This whole time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.91,1:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还在生气吗? - 都过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You're okay with it? - It's in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.24,1:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,生气有什么用?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.42,1:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那好 - 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.71,1:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢你 彼得 - 嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Thanks, Peter. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.71,1:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 那我们就上路吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay. Okay. Let's just hit the road then, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.26,1:17:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你抱着桑尼 我来开车 - 我马上抓住他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- You get Sonny, and I'll drive. - I'll grab him in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.38,1:17:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我杀了你再说! - 哎唷!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- After I fucking kill you! - Ow!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.55,1:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You little thief prick.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.06,1:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧 混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Die, thief. You thief.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.39,1:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别激动啊!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.85,1:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得 从1数到10 能帮助你消气!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter, count to 1 0. It'll help. Aah!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.94,1:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你电话响了!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}The phone's ringing!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.95,1:18:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 亲爱的 - 彼得 我要生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Hello, dear. - Peter, it's happening.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.49,1:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么? - 我的羊水破了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- What? - You won't believe it. My water broke.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.00,1:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么会? - 你在哪里?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- How? - Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.50,1:18:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我在大峡谷 我马上就到那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'm at the Grand Canyon. I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.17,1:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 你说你在大峡谷?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What? Did you just say the Grand Canyon?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.59,1:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Peter?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.84,1:18:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妈 他说他在大峡谷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Mom? He's at the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.18,1:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.18,1:18:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁的电话? - 我老婆要生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Who was it? - My wife has gone into labor.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.39,1:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她不是要剖腹产吗? - 快上车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I thought we were having a C- section. - Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.94,1:18:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你踩到我的名牌皮鞋了 好啦 好啦!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You stepped on my Capezios. Okay, okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.02,1:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.11,1:18:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你真是个疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Good God, you maniac.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.46,1:18:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来不及了 真棒 我将要错过我的孩子的诞生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Not gonna make it. That's great. I'm gonna miss the birth of my child.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.05,1:18:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来的及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We are gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.30,1:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谁跟你 我们啊? 不要说"我们"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}There's no "we." Don't say "we."
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.47,1:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好啦 看一下 首先... - 能让我先说吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Okay, look... No. Me first. - Please, can I...?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.18,1:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 你不能 我说过我会发火的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No. You can't. I told you I saw red.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.48,1:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过我会揍你的 这是我毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I told you I was gonna put hands on you. I have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.06,1:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,并且很遗憾地 你成了受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}And I'm sorry you were the recipient of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.65,1:19:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我警告过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.19,1:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm sorry. - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.24,1:19:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是将来我们 关系变好的时候...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}But in the future, when we're hanging out as buddies...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.24,1:19:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们闹了矛盾 别打我的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...if we get into a fight, don't go for my face.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.53,1:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好不好! 我靠这张脸吃饭 - 可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- That's how I make a living. Okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.54,1:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还没止血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Still bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.12,1:19:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看看置物箱 应该有急救药箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Check the glove, there's probably a first- aid kit or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.38,1:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己清理一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Clean yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.76,1:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一只家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Check this thing out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.52,1:19:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.86,1:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信这是我干的!!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I can't believe I did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.36,1:20:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 彼得 非常抱歉!!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sorry, Peter. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.74,1:20:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到里面有子弹 不好意思 快停车吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I didn't think it was loaded. Pull over.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.37,1:20:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行 我要一直走 - 不 开到路边吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- No, I wanna keep going. - No. Pull over.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.45,1:20:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不想耽搁 - 停到路边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I don't want to. - Pull over.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.95,1:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是真的 不是真的! 到底是为什么啊!?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No, it didn't happen, it didn't happen! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.54,1:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我震惊啊! - 我疼死了!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm in shock! - It burns!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.96,1:20:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,开到路边! 开到路边!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Pull over! Pull over!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.88,1:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌! 别慌!不要恐慌!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Don't panic! Don't panic! Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.27,1:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 不要 - 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Oh, no. - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.27,1:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一枪正好打在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's right there, yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.65,1:20:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的非常抱歉 - 没关系啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'm so sorry. - Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.23,1:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须先止血 把你的围巾拿来做止血带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We gotta stop the bleeding. I need your scarf.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.48,1:20:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我要转身吗? - 不 不用 做止血带 止血带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Turn around? - No. No, a tourniquet. A tourniquet.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.99,1:20:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你又干什么啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}What the fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.61,1:20:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,转身啊! 冷静啦 我来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Turn around! Stay still. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.37,1:20:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你来系它 我只有一只手能用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're fine. Right here. I need you to tie it. I only got one hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.37,1:20:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口很深的 必须送你到医院去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's deep. We gotta get you to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.79,1:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就是要去医院 没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're going to a hospital. We're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.13,1:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 天啊 !我做了什么啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, God! What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.63,1:21:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别慌张 慢慢来 - 我做了什么啊? 我做了什么啊?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Stop freaking out. It's okay. - What did I do? What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.96,1:21:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们像在厕所一样 练习一下 好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Let's do a little acting exercise like we did at the rest stop in the bathroom, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.22,1:21:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你是排长 我是你的士兵...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}You're a sergeant, I'm just a grunt in your platoon...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.97,1:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你保证 把我送回情人的身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}...but you promised me that you'd get me home to my high- school sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.68,1:21:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.64,1:21:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,开拍!!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Action.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.23,1:21:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 彼得 - 嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Peter. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.53,1:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我呕吐在你的伤口上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I puked on the wound.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.20,1:21:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 没关系 伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I know. It's okay, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.07,1:21:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你来开车 我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I need you to drive, but we gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.57,1:21:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.66,1:21:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.67,1:21:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,到后座上去 士兵 难道你是娘们还是其他的?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Get in the back seat, private. What are you, a girl or something?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.50,1:21:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好极了 - 就这样吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Excellent. - Like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.84,1:21:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对了 快走吧 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Yeah, let's roll. - Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.38,1:22:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想出来了吗? - 想什么出来?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Figured it out yet? - Figured what out?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.51,1:22:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子要出生了 取什么名字?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Your son's about to be born. What will you name him?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.05,1:22:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等生下来就知道了 - 桑尼! 这名字怎么样?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I'll know it when I see him. - How about "Sonny"?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.89,1:22:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不能让我儿子 和一条自慰的狗同一个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No. Not naming my son after a masturbating dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.81,1:22:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要听他胡说 桑尼 他喜欢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Don't listen to him, Sonny. He loves you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.56,1:22:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,桑尼 不要!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sonny, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.64,1:22:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,桑尼 对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sonny. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.40,1:22:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回家了!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We're heading home!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.75,1:23:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,终于赶到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.25,1:23:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 来吧 - 我赶到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Okay, come on. - I made it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.50,1:23:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 猴子 猴子 忘了猴子!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, the monkey, the monkey, the monkey.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.09,1:23:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,桑尼 稍等一下 马上回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sonny, we'll be right back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.68,1:23:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.51,1:23:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 干!!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.93,1:23:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.52,1:23:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个要当父亲的 还中了枪 应该??\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I have an expectant father and a gunshot victim.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.02,1:23:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道要去哪儿 就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I know where we're going. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.98,1:23:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在左拐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Then we cut left.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.94,1:23:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 糟糕了 - 怎么了?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Shoot. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.45,1:23:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记为桑尼 开扇窗户了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I forgot to crack a window for Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.61,1:23:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 连车门都没了 伊森 - 对啊 那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- The door's off the car, Ethan. - Right. Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.49,1:23:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 咱们在一块 什么都能考虑到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}See? Together we think of everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.29,1:23:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我们到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.46,1:23:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来 给你整理一下 - 应该的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Let's get you cleaned up. Right? - Great. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.01,1:23:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Give me these guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.13,1:24:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就好看多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's all about to go down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.22,1:24:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给你一件背心 把血盖上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Give you a vest, cover up the blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.73,1:24:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过 我喜欢你的烫发了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Have I told you that I love your perm?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.32,1:24:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Thank you, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.65,1:24:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看你精神好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Look who's come around.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.82,1:24:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.61,1:24:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 来 到这里来 我们到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}No, come on, come on. This way, this way. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.33,1:24:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 - 好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Ma'am. - Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.91,1:24:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的手铐放进口袋里 藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Put your handcuffs in your pocket. Hide them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.41,1:24:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是给你的猴子 - 真多人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Here's the Rally Monkey. - Boom.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.46,1:24:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 喔~~ - 深呼吸 用力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Ohh! - Just keep pushing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.17,1:24:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Sarah?
