Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.47,1:26:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不太明白 什么..? - 算了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- I don't get it. What...? - Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.55,1:26:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这....这...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's... It's....
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.89,1:26:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是个好兆头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}It's gotta be a good sign.
