Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.67,1:27:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会留着的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I'll keep it handy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.01,1:27:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这几天真是疯狂啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We had a crazy few days.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.43,1:27:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太疯狂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}That was nuts.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.89,1:27:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果以后有时间 再一起长途旅行吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}We should do it again. Go across country again.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.10,1:27:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.73,1:27:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然 - 考虑好了明天给我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- Sure. - Call me tomorrow about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.35,1:27:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果我不的话 - 明天给我打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}- If I don't... - Call me tomorrow about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.36,1:27:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以用电子邮件给你 请不要介意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs50.556\b0}I might e- mail you. Please don't take it personally.
